001package edu.cnm.deepdive.teamle.model;
002
003import com.google.gson.annotations.Expose;
004import com.google.gson.annotations.SerializedName;
005import java.util.LinkedList;
006import java.util.List;
007
008/**
009 * Gets all sports/ leagues from a specific country.
010 */
011public class Country {
012
013  @Expose
014  @SerializedName("name_en")
015  private final String name;
016  private final List<League> leagues = new LinkedList<>();
017
018  /**
019   * Gets a specific country
020   */
021  public Country() {
022    name = null;
023  }
024
025  /**
026   * gets name of selected country
027   * @return String name
028   */
029  public String getName() {
030    return name;
031  }
032
033  /**
034   * Gets list of leagues in a specific country
035   * @return List<Leagues>
036   */
037  public List<League> getLeagues() {
038    return leagues;
039  }
040}
